    T - expression type

    DateTimeOperation, DateTimePath, DateTimeSubQuery, DateTimeTemplate

    public abstract class DateTimeExpression<T extends Comparable>
extends TemporalExpression<T>
    DateTimeExpression represents Date / Time expressions The date representation is compatible with the Gregorian calendar.
    Author:
    tiwe
    See Also:
    Gregorian calendar, Serialized Form
